---
layout: layout.njk
title: Brian Lovin — About
description: About Brian Lovin — Software designer and developer portfolio, work history, and speaking details.
pageType: about
---
<div class="animate-in">
  <img src="{{ about.avatar }}" alt="{{ site.name }}" class="about-avatar">
  
  <div class="about-bio">
    {% for paragraph in about.bioParagraphs %}
    <p>{{ paragraph | safe }}</p>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Social Media Links -->
